title: Holiday Hug'ems - 6 Soft Huggable Holiday Characters to Crochet
description: Stuffed animals have never been cuter or put to better use. These adorable crocheted creations wrap their arms around their own individually designed fleece blankets. The patterns aren't just for animals: easy directions are given to make the fleece blankets, all with their own unique edgings. St. Nick is ready for Christmas gifting. Snowman makes a cozy addition to any winter wonderland. Penguin will cuddle underneath his own penguin print blanket. Scarecrow will help with a little rest during harvest time. Bunny is ready to retire after the Easter egg hunt and Uncle Sam Bear will keep you company during fireworks on the Fourth! Any holiday is made more special with a hug, and a holiday hug'em is even better
